OL,3,CBaby loss certificates to be made
OL,4,Cavailable in Wales next year
OL,6,FParents who lose a baby during
OL,7,Fpregnancy will be a able to receive a
OL,8,Fcertificate to acknowledge their
OL,9,Fexperience in Wales, the Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment has announced.
OL,12,FPreviously, in England, those who had
OL,13,Flost a baby before 24 weeks of
OL,14,Fpregnancy were able to apply for baby
OL,15,Floss certificates, but there was no
OL,16,Fsimilar scheme in Wales.
