OL,3,CBaby loss certificates to be made
OL,4,Cavailable in Wales next year
OL,6,FThe UK Government launched the
OL,7,Fcertificate scheme in February 2024
OL,8,Ffor parents who had experienced loss
OL,9,Fsince September 2018. It later amended
OL,10,Fthe scheme so there would be no time
OL,11,Flimit on the initiative, so
OL,12,Fcertificates would become available
OL,13,Ffor any parent who had experienced a
OL,14,Floss before 24 weeks, or 28 weeks if
OL,15,Fthe loss was before October 1992.
OL,17,FAs of January 2025, the UK Government
OL,18,Fsaid it had issued 95,017 certificates.
