OL,3,CBaby loss certificates to be made
OL,4,Cavailable in Wales next year
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government now says a
OL,7,Fsimilar service will be available in
OL,8,FWales in 2026 - two years after
OL,9,FEngland's introduction.
OL,11,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"The loss of a baby at any stage of
OL,13,Fpregnancy is devastating. We are
OL,14,Fcommitted to ensuring every family is
OL,15,Fproperly supported during this time.
