OL,3,CBaby loss certificates to be made
OL,4,Cavailable in Wales next year
OL,6,F"All families who experience pregnancy
OL,7,Floss at maternity units in Wales are
OL,8,Fsupported by bereavement midwives, in
OL,9,Fconjunction with the charity Sands,
OL,10,Fand offered memory boxes, which
OL,11,Finclude a certificate of birth.
OL,13,F"We have recently directed the NHS
OL,14,FBusiness Services Authority to extend
OL,15,Fthe bereavement certificate service to
OL,16,Fpeople in Wales. We expect these to be
OL,17,Favailable next year."
